DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Toronto Public Library - S. Walter Stewart Bran
 ch for a discussion with cycling advocates working to make Toronto cycling
 -friendly. Learn how you can become involved in advocating for safer bikin
 g conditions in our community. Whether you're a seasoned cyclist or just s
 tarting out\, this event is for you. Let's work together to make our city 
 a safer place for cyclists!\n\nPanel discussion followed by a Q&A period.\
 n\n(http://eventbrite.ca/e/taking-action-for-safe-cycling-in-the-city-tick
 ets-1797500766179?aff=ebdssbdestsearch&keep_tld=1) Register here\n\n#block
 -29ffe2c2873cb8a30b90 { --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px\; --twe
