DESCRIPTION:(https://www.westscarboroughrailpath.ca/) West Scarborough Rai
 l Path (WSRP)\n\nCommunity Bikeways is one of the featured speakers\, and 
 will present the Loop Trail initiative and talk about why it's an opportun
 e time --- given Doug Ford's edict against new bike lanes that reduce car 
 lanes --- to be connecting the strands of bike paths across the city that 
 could become useful utilitarian routes. The Loop Trail and the WSRP are co
 mplementary initiatives.\n\n#block-020448911272b5b4a8a1 { --tweak-text-blo
 ck-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px\; --tweak-text-block-radius: unset\; --stroke-s
